  "intent_precise": "Twist Library Prep || Part 3: PCR Amplification: Using pcr_plate (pcr_plate, slot 1), rsvr (labware, slot 8), kapa_labware (labware, slot 5), Twist UDI Plate (pcr_plate, slot 4). With cold_mod module, mag_version module. (1) Set temperature to 4\u00b0C. (2) Pause: Please replace tips (3) Transfer from source to destination. (4) Mix mix_times times. (5) Transfer from source (A1, A1) to destination (A1, A1). (6) Pause: msg1 (7) Transfer 50\u00b5L from source to destination. (8) Mix 10 times at 90\u00b5L. (9) Incubate for 5 minutes. (10) Engage magnets for bead separation. (11) Incubate for 1 minutes. (12) Transfer 100\u00b5L from source to destination. (13) Transfer 200\u00b5L from source to destination. (14) Incubate for 1 minutes. (15) Transfer 200\u00b5L from source to destination. (16) Incubate for 5 minutes. (17) Disengage magnets to release beads. (18) Transfer 22\u00b5L from source to destination. (19) Mix 5 times at 20\u00b5L. (20) Incubate for 2 minutes. (21) Engage magnets for bead separation. (22) Incubate for 3 minutes. (23) Transfer 20\u00b5L from source to destination.",
  "intent_concise": "Perform magnetic bead separation, temperature control (4\u00b0C). (volumes 20\u00b5L-200\u00b5L, ~18 min total)",
  "intent": "For the Twist Library Prep PCR Amplification step, start by setting up your deck with the PCR plate in slot 1, reservoir in slot 8, KAPA reagents in slot 5, and Twist UDI plate in slot 4, then set the cold module to 4\u00b0C and replace your tips before beginning transfers. You'll need to transfer reagents between A1 wells, add 50\u00b5L volumes with 10x mixing at 90\u00b5L, then perform magnetic bead separations with 1-5 minute incubations as specified - engaging magnets for 1 and 3 minutes during the two separation steps. The protocol includes several 200\u00b5L and 100\u00b5L transfers between engagement cycles, and finishes with a 22\u00b5L transfer, 5x mixing at 20\u00b5L volume, followed by a final 2-minute incubation and 20\u00b5L collection after the last 3-minute magnetic separation.",
